comments: You'll have a total of four critiques, but as long as you work at a consistent pace you'll be prepared.
Intermediate Digital Photo is a wonderful photography class. It picks up where you left of in intro digital, but gives you a lot more creative freedom in working on whatever you like.

It's like intro, but with more freedom to work on your interests, and more individualized technical instruction. I definitely recommend it if you want to continue to work on your own projects and still receive regular guidance.
A great opportunity to expand your technical skills while focusing them on an individual project.
